          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural Ir (50um)",
                "high purity metalic foils"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "LEGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Low Energy Photon Spectrometer, LEPS"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "EDEG",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Thick, 50um, Ir foils were",
                "irradiated with alpha beam of different energies to",
                "measure tick target yield. (13.4-17 MeV)",
                "Irradiation were done in a Faraday-cup like",
                "targetholder with beam intensity of I=2.0 - 2.5 uA,",
                "for 22.0-34.0h duration.",
                "The beam intensity was monitored and registered in",
                "every minutes.",
                "No chemical separation was applied.",
                "Several series of spectra were recorded to",
                "be able to follow the decay. Gamma- and X-ray spectra",
                "were recorded.",
                "Decay data were taken from NUDAT online data library.",
                "Correction for attenuation of low energy gamma photons",
                "in the Ir target foils was done."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The energy error contains the beam energy",
                "uncertainty of 0.3% and an additional 0.5% uncertainty,",
                "which accounts for the considered energy dependence and",
                "fit un-certainty of the yield."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainty of the thick target yields",
                "are estimated in the  standard way as the square root",
                "of the quadratic summation of the independently",
                "contributing parameters."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
